---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="LoveAlwaysHere 首页" description="个人博客与工具集">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-40 -left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-60 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-violet-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <section class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-16 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-cyan-500/20 bg-cyan-500/5 text-cyan-400 text-xs tracking-wider mb-8">&#x2b50; 个人空间 · 技术博客 · 实用工具</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 via-cyan-400 to-violet-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">探索 · 创造 · 分享</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">记录技术思考，分享实用工具。</p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 text-white font-medium shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/25 transition-all hover:scale-105">浏览博客 &#8594;</a>
        <a href="/tools" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 text-gray-300 font-medium hover:border-cyan-500/50 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-all hover:scale-105">实用工具</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-cyan-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 to-cyan-600/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">&#x1f4dd;</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-2">技术博客</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">记录前端、全栈开发中的踩坑与思考，分享技术心得与最佳实践。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-violet-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-violet-600/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">&#x1f527;</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-2">实用工具</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">日常开发和生活所需的在线小工具，开箱即用，持续更新。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-amber-500/30 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/20 to-amber-600/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">&#x1f680;</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-2">持续进化</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">不断迭代优化，让这个小小的数字花园越来越丰富。</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>